summary: Swedish master student with an extensive academic background spanning over three continents and four languages. Robust professional experience from both private and public sector in stakeholder management, qualitative research, and standardization of processes. Co-founder and former leader of various projects in diverse cities related to global issues as well as to students’ well-being. Passionate about innovative sustainable solutions.
